3 ml/min;



Detection:
uv, 270 nm;



Temperature:
ambient.

[0086] (B) The racemic product of Example 1 (26 mg) was subjected to preparative HPLC under the following conditions:
2
Column: ASTEC cyclobond I acetyl, 250 × 4.6 mm;
Eluant: 0.2% triethylammonium acetate (prepared by adding glacial
acetic acid to 0.2% triethylamine in water, to a final pH
7.2);
Flow: 2 ml/min;
Detection: uv, 300 nm;
Temperature: ambient.
